com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.block.tileentity

Class TileEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.JsRegisteredClass
      • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.MinecraftClassWrapper
        • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.block.tileentity.TileEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IWrapper

    public class TileEntity
extends MinecraftClassWrapper
    Wraps around the Minecraft tile entities to allow for calls to the Minecraft tile entity methods and fields. TileEntity can be instantiated with the single Object constructor. This takes a Javascript object that can contain the following properties.

    // called every tick to update the tile entity
    update : function(tickAge, world, blockPos, nbtData)

    // called when the tile entity is created
    init : function(world, blockPos, nbtData)
    Author:
    pcr3w
